!theme aws-orange
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor Browser

package \"API Gateway\" {
 [POST /jobs] as PostJobs
 [GET /jobs] as GetJobs
 [GET /jobs/{id}] as GetJobId
}

package \"Producer Lambda\" {
 [Insert job to DynamoDB] as InsertDynamo
 [Send message to SQS] as SendSQS
}

package \"Job Queue (SQS)\" {
 [Job Queue]
}

package \"Worker Lambda\" {
 [Query Athena Workgroup] as QueryAthena
 [Update DynamoDB with result] as UpdateDynamo
}

package \"Athena\" {
 [annotations_parquet table]
}

package \"DynamoDB\" {
 [Job Table]
}

package \"CloudWatch\" {
 [API Logs]
}

Browser --> PostJobs
Browser --> GetJobs
Browser --> GetJobId

PostJobs --> InsertDynamo
PostJobs --> SendSQS
GetJobs --> InsertDynamo
GetJobId --> InsertDynamo

SendSQS --> [Job Queue]
[Job Queue] --> QueryAthena
QueryAthena --> [annotations_parquet table]
QueryAthena --> UpdateDynamo
InsertDynamo --> [Job Table]
UpdateDynamo --> [Job Table]

PostJobs --> [API Logs]
